## Lab-Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelets: The Value Case

This is the section I want men to read twice. The four-prong lab-grown diamond tennis bracelet is currently 30% off across all carat weights, and Blue Nile discloses the quality: **F-G color, VS2-SI1 clarity.** That is specific and verifiable — not "premium quality" or "hand-selected." F-G is near-colorless. VS2-SI1 is eye-clean in all standard four-prong settings.

[![Men's lab diamond tennis bracelet in 14k white gold on wrist, Blue Nile lifestyle photo](/images/mens-lab-diamond-tennis-bracelet-white-gold.avif)](/images/mens-lab-diamond-tennis-bracelet-white-gold.avif)

The equivalent natural tennis bracelet at the same carat weight costs 3–4× more. For a bracelet worn daily at arm's length, no one distinguishes lab from natural in a four-prong setting.

